{"timestamp": "2025-12-02 17:18:59.573244", "event": "llm_end", "text": "Submission accepted.\n\nSummary of submitted solution:\n- is_anomaly: true\n- Faulty devices localized: host_2_1_1_1, host_2_2_2_1, host_1_2_2_1\n- Root cause(s) selected: host_static_blackhole, icmp_acl_block, receiver_resource_contention\n\nNotes:\n- host_static_blackhole and icmp_acl_block correspond to the \"unknown\" (null) reachability results concentrated on specific hosts — likely measurement-agent filtering, local firewall/ICMP policy, or probe script issues.\n- receiver_resource_contention corresponds to the intermittent high latency/jitter observed on a small subset of host→host and host→service flows.", "generation_info": {"finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 2689, "output_tokens": 150, "total_tokens": 2839, "input_token_details": {"audio": 0, "cache_read": 1664}, "output_token_details": {"audio": 0, "reasoning": 0}}}
